WEBVTT

00:00:00.794 --> 00:00:01.960
I love fashion.

00:00:02.693 --> 00:00:06.622
I actually go to bed every night
thinking about what I'm going to wear

00:00:06.646 --> 00:00:07.865
the next day.

00:00:08.549 --> 00:00:10.992
Clothing transforms me,

00:00:11.016 --> 00:00:12.578
defines me,

00:00:12.602 --> 00:00:14.052
gives me confidence.

00:00:14.769 --> 00:00:17.356
You may not feel
the same way about fashion,

00:00:17.380 --> 00:00:23.702
but I bet you have a favorite T-shirt
or a pair of jeans that transforms you --

00:00:23.726 --> 00:00:25.253
makes you feel good,

00:00:25.277 --> 00:00:27.006
makes you feel confident,

00:00:27.030 --> 00:00:28.649
makes you feel like you.

00:00:29.480 --> 00:00:31.202
When I was younger,